OL,3,COne million vulnerable adults living
OL,4,Cin Dickensian cold homes this
OL,5,CChristmas, warn campaigners
OL,7,FMore than one million of the UK's most
OL,8,Fvulnerable adults will be living in
OL,9,F"Dickensian" cold and damp homes this
OL,10,FChristmas, campaigners have warned.
OL,12,FSome 16% of adults overall, or 8.3
OL,13,Fmillion people, are living in cold and
OL,14,Fdamp homes in the UK.
OL,16,FFrom hypothermia to respiratory
OL,17,Finfections and dementia they are all
OL,18,Fexposed to health complications which
OL,19,Fcome from living in fuel poverty,
OL,20,Faccording to the Warm this Winter
OL,21,Fcampaign.
